title: Humpty Dumpty had a great fall
text: And hopefully they can put Humpty together again. A Humpty Dumpty figure at a mini-golf course near Ithaca was allegedly stolen by college students camping nearby. But this tale may have a happy ending: He was recovered, and the suspects have been caught.
